bite problem'' _ basically, his rabbits without the giant ears. `` Maybe someday <PERSON> Marge </PERSON> will take off a wig and reveal her true identity,'' he teased. <PERSON> Groening </PERSON> said he does fervently hope that <PERSON> Binky </PERSON> and the other rabbits from `` Life in Hell'' might get their own TV series, too, someday. `` Someday,'' <PERSON> Groening </PERSON> said, `` maybe television will be ready for my hellish stuff.''
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
