<FIRST>r f PM-FoxRestructuring Bjt   07-13 0498</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Fox Restructuring, Bjt,0518</SECOND>
<HEAD>Fox Restructures Film, Television Units, Hires New Studio Chief</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JOHN HORN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
